About guile-gtksourceview
===================

guile-gtksourceview is a Guile wrapper for gtksourceview. It is a part
of GNU guile-gnome.


Build dependencies
==================

Guile-GtkSourceView requires GtkSourceView 1.8.0 development packages.

guile-gnome-gtksourceview depends on guile-gnome-glib, which is commonly
distributed with the `guile-gnome-platform' tarball.  See
http://gnu.org/s/guile-gnome/, for more.


Copying guile-gtksourceview
=====================

Distribution of guile-gtksourceview is under the GPL.  See the COPYING file
for more information.


Contact info
============

  Mailing List: guile-gtk-general@gnu.org
  Homepage:     http://www.gnu.org/software/guile-gnome/
  Download:     http://www.gnu.org/software/guile-gnome/download/


Installation quickstart
=======================

Install using the standard autotools incantation:
  ./configure && make && make install.

If you are building from git, you will need to run ./autogen.sh first.

You can run without installing, just run './dev-environ guile'.


